<div>
    <!-- Banner -->
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center h-96">
        <img src={Hero1.src} alt="Triaso" class="" />
    </div>
    <!-- Contenido -->
    <div class="lg:pt-80 md:pt-80">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 space-y-5">
            <div class="flex justify-end items-center">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl uppercase">
                    Some Tips for Buying an Asphalt Plant
                </h1>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-5">
                <div>
                    <p class="font-bold text-xl text-[#393939]">
                        Purchasing an asphalt plant is a significant investment
                        and serves as the foundation of an asphalt mix
                        production business. Buy wisely.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pl-5">
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Be cautious with salespeople; they may say anything to
                        make a sale.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Dig deeper and investigate anything they can’t answer
                        immediately or that doesn’t seem logical.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Compare the offerings from each supplier you are
                        considering.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Visit the manufacturer or supplier and verify every
                        claim they make.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Include us in your visit and verification process.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Assign these tasks to an experienced engineer or an
                        external consultant.
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-[#393939]">
                        Request plenty of references and verify that they are
                        legitimate.
                    </li>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Banner -->
        <div class="w-full bg-blueMain p-20 mt-5">
            <div
                class="max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row md:flex-row justify-between items-center"
            >
                <div>
                    <button
                        class="bg-white transition-all duration-300 ease-out transform hover:scale-105 p-5 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-5"
                    >
                        <span class="font-bold">Talk to a representative </span>
